{"tid":695567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 南美新娘潭　颱風天時熱爆網","createTime":"2018-06-09T10:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T10:23:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fad1ef17a61e440c1f7b5065ff5446a187b9cb3f","tid":695567,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:06:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180609/20415339\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F20415339&d=Wt0jbW76SMb%2FhzjzdAk9X8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=48e3ac3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F20415339&h=883509a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180609/20415339</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月09日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n南美新娘潭　颱風天時熱爆網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180609/large/a1402a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180609%2Flarge%2Fa1402a.gif&h=4b7deaee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■網上瘋傳的秘魯瀑布圖片，流水恍如披白紗的新娘。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n颱風襲港，連日帶來暴雨連場，社交網站昨日突然瘋傳一張瀑布照片，一道瀑布掛在山谷，流水飛瀉直下，遇石橫分，落到水潭底，在陽光下遠看瀑布，恍如一位披着白紗的新娘，側身含羞望向山中，妙不可言。有不少網民看到這像是含羞答答新娘的瀑布，自自然然想到就是大埔的新娘潭了，但原來是一場美麗的誤會。<br />\n<br />\n其實此奇景位於遠在南美的秘魯北部，當地人稱這瀑布為La Novia，據悉要徒步越過山野兩小時才能到達，瀑布圖片亦在外國的社交網站瘋傳，外國網民對這瀑布外觀嘖嘖稱奇，並稱之為Bride's Falls（新娘瀑布）。至於香港的新娘潭亦有她淒美的故事，相傳很久很久以前，有一名新娘乘坐花轎經過潭邊時，轎夫因路滑跣腳將新娘掉落瀑布下的水潭溺斃，因而得名。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港故事：玉器市場擺檔50年　草根一支筆　武生變文膽<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點●即聽"},{"pid":"e24eb2d30e8febb6dcf737dc7cb3d5e7253adfd6","tid":695567,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"真係好似"},{"pid":"0d2cda590c76e848605f228374d73503607b289b","tid":695567,"uid":104699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"仲要有波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港個新娘潭係咪無波"},{"pid":"a8327c6277f97da20c834e8a7975c5ba83a30016","tid":695567,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:23:51.000Z","msg":"啊！這是大自然的美啊！"}]}